// REPL (Read Evaluation Print Loops) is to execute small byte size code. Like Console of chrome developer tool.
// Type in hyper, to enter into REPL
node

// If we enter "con" and press tab two times then REPL will show all the related commands.

// If we enter "console." and press tab two times, then it will show related commands.

console.log("Hey there!");    // Press Enter then, it will executes that line of code.

// To exit from REPL type OR press "CTRL + C" two times.
.exit

// To clear screen and remove previous commands.
clear
